metadata.name: Infinite Memorial
metadata.description:
Collaboration with Isa Indra Permana

These photos bring back those good times. Reminds friendships are built by magical bonds. Moments whether it’s jokes or sharing food, or just fun conversation, no matter how apart they are, the heart knows its valuable friends. Friendship is built on a foundation of mutual trust, pillars that have the perspective that is in line with each other, the interior of the same interest, and a roof where we are always safe when sheltered.

3543 × 3543px, RGB, digital, November 2022
